        <abstract>
            <p>Asks to be informed whenever more copies of his books are printed, as there may be errors to correct.</p> 
<p>Asks how many copies of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> have been printed "from the first". The number will be "a good puff" when listed in the new edition of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p> 
